      "name": "Pathfinder #202: Severed at the Root",
      "page": 85,
      "type": "source"
    }
  ],
  "text": "Woodblessed are those granted uncontrollable energy drawn from the Plane of Wood\u2014a blessing that brings pain and eventual death.",
  "type": "monster_family"
}